==English==
===Etymology===
From {{Arab.}} {{ARchar|فم الحوت}} (''fam al-ḥūt'') ‘the whale's mouth’, from {{ARchar|[[فم]]}} ‘mouth’ + {{ARchar|[[حوت]]}} ‘whale’.

===Noun===
{{wikipedia|Fomalhaut}}
'''Formalhaut'''

#{{star}}: The brightest [[star]] in the [[constellation]] [[Piscis Austrinus]] and one of the brightest stars in the night sky; Alpha (α) Piscis Austrini.